<dec f='include/theora/codec.h' l='540' type='void th_comment_add(th_comment * _tc, char * _comment)'/>
<doc f='include/theora/codec.h' l='531'>/**Add a comment to an initialized #th_comment structure.
 * \note Neither th_comment_add() nor th_comment_add_tag() support
 *  comments containing null values, although the bitstream format does
 *  support them.
 * To add such comments you will need to manipulate the #th_comment
 *  structure directly.
 * \param _tc      The #th_comment struct to add the comment to.
 * \param _comment Must be a null-terminated UTF-8 string containing the
 *                  comment in &quot;TAG=the value&quot; form.*/</doc>
